'''Itsembabwoko ry'u Rwanda ry'1994''' ryari kwica kw'[[Abatutsi]] na kw'[[Abahutu]] bakomye Abatutsi kuva itariki ya 06 Mata 1994 kugeza Nyakanga 1994. Kw'itariki ya 06 Mata 1994 ni mugoroba, indege ya [[Perezida]] [[Habyarimana Yuvenari]] yamanukishijwe, ariko ntituzi abicanyi bari bande. Vuba, ingabo nyinshi zatangiye kwica Abatutsi. Minisitiri w'Intebe, [[Uwiringiyimana Agati]] yicwa n'ingabo kandi ingabo cumi Zibirigi yicwa. Munsi wose, abandi Batutsi bicwa. Benshi bicwa mu nsengero na mu mashuri na mu mavuriro. Abatutsi biswe 'inyenzi'. Mirisiya imwe yari [[Interahamwe]], kandi indi yari [[Impuzamugambi]]. Nyamara, abantu benshi ntibari mu mirisiya bica inshuti n'abaturanyi bye. Kw'itariki ya 04 Nyakanga 1994, Inkotanyi bageze i [[Kigali]]. Abantu gahumbagiza bicwa.

Uyu munsi, [[Kagame Pawuro]],muyobozi w'Inkotanyi, ari Perezida y'u Rwanda. Abicanyi n'abere byinshi byasubiye ku Rwanda mu myaka y'1997 na y'1998. None, hari amahoro mu [[Rwanda]].
